    "\n",
    "**Key facts from my certificate and transcript:**\n",
    "- Overall grade: **3.5 (satisfactory)**\n",
    "- Total credits: **180 CP** (completed within the regular study period)\n",
    "- Bachelor thesis: \"Development of a Cross-domain Knowledge Base for Cyber Intelligence in Smart Grids\" – **grade 3.0**\n",
    "- Examiner: Univ.-Prof. Dr. Andreas Ulbig"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
